Output Guard Validation Pipeline. LLM Output -> Length Limit (4096 chars) -> Truncate Flag -> Content Safety Check (GPT-4o-mini Judge: "violent, insulting, discriminatory, illegal") -> Block/Safe -> Schema Validation (Pydantic JSON Schema) -> Valid/Invalid -> Final Output. Safety Check Prompt: "Check for: violence, insults, discrimination, illegal content. Answer ONLY 'OK' or 'BLOCKED: <category>'." Schema Validation: Required keys, type checking. German labels.